After 1 month 1/2 of work,Ill send you my new map :D

The scene takes place in a spaceship somewhere in the galaxy. There are 2 times in my map. First with all lights on, during 7 minutes to simulate a good atmosphere with asteroids crashing on the ship, and after this time all the lights shut down, black out during 20s with alarm sound and voice, and after this 20s, red alarm lights switch on. (sorry for my english :D), dont' panic !!!!!!!!!!

Just play and enjoy it !
